content.rendered:
The Cube Corp. Raid Den can be accessed by heading down towards the dock from the Cube Corp building, then using Surf towards the right to reach the hidden area east of the corporation. When you see a small patch of land then disembark and examine the narrow gap between the trees to find the den.
